"orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadaArN","text_ar":"قَدَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sgh, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qidaArN","text_ar":"قِدَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadaArapN","text_ar":"قَدَارَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quduwrapN","text_ar":"قُدُورَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quduwrN","text_ar":"قُدُورٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Power; ability."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadarotu","text_ar":"قَدَرْتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY Al$~aYo'i","text_ar":"عَلَى الشَّىْءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  Hence, (TA,) the first and second and third and fourth (S, * Msb, * TA) and fifth, (K, TA,) or all excepting"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadarN","text_ar":"قَدَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqodarN","text_ar":"مَقْدَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TK,) [and there seems to be no reason for not adding these two,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Competence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sufficiency; richness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * Msb, * K.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN *uw qudorapK","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ ذُو قُدْرَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqoduwrapK","text_ar":"مَقْدُورَةٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqodarapK","text_ar":"مَقْدَرَةٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqodirap","text_ar":"مَقْدِرَة","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man possessing competence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"riches."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","Ks","Fr","Akh","TA","Sgh","Lh","TK"]},{"entry_id":"n35283","headword_ar":"قَدَرَةٌ","root":"qdr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain interval,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distance, between every two palm-trees."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, Sgh, K.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naxolN gurisa EalaY Alqadarapi","text_ar":"نَخْلٌ غُرِسَ عَلَى القَدَرَةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Palm-trees planted at the fixed distance, one from another."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, Sgh, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kamo qadarapu naxolika","text_ar":"كَمْ قَدَرَةُ نَخْلِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What is the fixed distance of thy palm-trees, one from another?"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (K.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}